bctoolbox
------------------------------------------
Utilities library used by Belledonne Communications softwares like belle-sip,
mediastreamer2 and linphone.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.1.7-1
  libbctoolbox-devel-4.4.0-1bl1
  libbctoolbox1-4.4.0-1bl1
  libbcunit-devel-3.0.2+git20200821-1bl1
  libbcunit0-3.0.2+git20200821-1bl1
  libgcc1-10.2.0-1
  libiconv2-1.16-2
  libmbedcrypto5-2.23.0-1
  libmbedtls13-2.23.0-1
  libmbedx509_1-2.23.0-1
  libstdc++6-10.2.0-1
  pkg-config-1.6.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.34+1git.de9c1b7cfe-1
  cmake-3.17.3-2
  cygport-0.34.0-1
  gcc-core-10.2.0-1
  gcc-g++-10.2.0-1
  gcc-objc++-10.2.0-1
  ninja-1.10.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://gitlab.linphone.org/BC/public/bctoolbox

Canonical download:
  https://gitlab.linphone.org/BC/public/bctoolbox/-/archive/4.4.0/bctoolbox-4.4.0.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack bctoolbox-4.4.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./bctoolbox-4.4.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/bctoolbox-4.4.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/bctoolbox-4.4.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbctoolbox1-4.4.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbctoolbox-devel-4.4.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

